@Reasoning
Set the optional description string. The pointer is adopted; the manifest
deallocates it on destroy_deep.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Store at offset 24.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Replacing a non-null description without first freeing it leaks memory;
caller responsibility.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "manifest_set_description" takes m as Integer, description as Integer returns Integer:
    If m is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    proc memory_set_int64 from Memory with m, 24, description
    Return 1
End Process

@Reasoning
Expose the description string.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Load offset 24.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 if not set.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "manifest_description" takes m as Integer returns Integer:
